              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "Say whether the following statements are true or false.\na) In the USA, people selling products never advertise through the media.\nb) The power of argument is mastered by advertisers to convince the public.\nc) Persuasion is the capacity of convincing others.\nd) Less than 50% of magazines and billboards consist of advertising."
            },
            {
              "id": "shared2011_s1_comp_q1_solution_1",
              "role": "SOLUTION",
              "type": "paragraph",
              "value": "a) F    b) T    c) T    d) F"
